{"type":"message","id":"e4e0be8a","parentId":"22a11ecb","timestamp":"2026-03-27T17:38:58.501Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The only session is the current cron session itself. There are no other active user conversations in the last 5 minutes. So I should execute the self-learning task.\n\nLet me search for latest news on 企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务.","thinkingSignature":"4208b48983f09f07a5c9afee03476b19b19d25adbaf24b5ab4c9bec6347bd4f7"},{"type":"text","text":"\n当前仅有本cron会话，无用户活跃对话，执行自主学习。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rfbun1dlh3q5_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":805,"output":111,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44897,"cost":{"input":0.0002415,"output":0.00013319999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0016941299999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774633133999}}
