{"type":"message","id":"8cbd598d","parentId":"e7081612","timestamp":"2026-03-27T17:40:38.019Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done! I've completed the self-learning task. Let me summarize what was done.","thinkingSignature":"8e7287ce599e5cdb05770c152ebc275f9801c2e8ef6d259c5a01966a686353bf"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n已无活跃对话（仅本cron会话），执行自主学习完成。\n\n**学习内容**：搜索了企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务等行业2026年最新动态，整理了9条关键信息，最终提炼为5条战略建议（分高/中优先级），已保存至 `/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md`。\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":6707,"output":106,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50794,"cost":{"input":0.0020120999999999997,"output":0.0001272,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0034587299999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774633234268}}
